## *Step #5: Voting inference based on this novel* methodology

Using the ChatGPT-based natural methodology, it is possible to identify each candidate’s position on the political compass. It is also possible to calculate the distance between each individual and the candidate they voted for, providing a quantitative measure of ideological proximity.

## Econometric Model

Using a Logic model to stimate the MVP, it's possible to forcast the vote of the individual.

Following the next model, the predict of the votes are stimates:

$$
P(V_i = 1) = \frac{1}{1 + \exp\left( \gamma_0 + \alpha \cdot ( d_{\text{ideo}}^{iA} - d_{\text{ideo}}^{iB}) + \beta \cdot ( d_{\text{pol}}^{iA}  -  d_{\text{pol}}^{iB}) \right)} + \epsilon 
$$

